# Using RGB

Experiment with the RGB values in the CSS style sheet. 

# Do This

1.  Find the CSS rule-set in the style sheet that gives the h1 tag its style. Change _only_ the first 0 to 255.
2.  Find the CSS rule-set in the style sheet that gives the p tag its style. Change _only_ the second 0 to 255.
3.  Find the CSS rule-set in the style sheet that gives the h3 tag its style. Change _only_ the third 0 to 255.

